name: Examples
description: TI's SimpleLink CC13xx CC26xx SDK provides a comprehensive set of examples to help developers get started with the SimpleLink CC13xx CC26xx family of wireless microcontrollers. The SimpleLink CC13xx CC26xx SDK provides examples that cover how to use BLE5, DMM, Z-Stack, Proprietary RF, TI 15.4, TI-Drivers and other software included in the SDK.

name: Documents
description: The SimpleLink CC13xx CC26xx SDK comes with documentation for all of the supported software libraries included in the SDK. For a good overview of what documentation is available in the SimpleLink CC13xx CC26xx SDK, go to "Documentation Overview". To get started quickly with the SimpleLink CC13xx CC26xx SDK, go to "Quick Start Guide".
